| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5539 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0a933597-e180-5865-8a96-e33f8c0788b7"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
